text: Her cyð þæt Ælfred lareow hæfeð gefreolsad vii men.
And feorðe his broðor dohtor Colawis.
And seofunde Eþeredes sunu his agenes meges Ælsrig hatte.
Þas seofun men Ælfrid hæfeð gefreolsad Godes þonces & sancte Cuðberhtes for hine & for his wif Kolawis.
On alles sancte Cuðbertes heoredes gewitnysse.
And hwa þe þis ymbwende bereafige hine God twoegra þinga her lyfes & heofona rices.
